title: Battlechefs S01E01 Vigo WEBRip.x264-TVC.mp4
description:
This brand new, unique cooking competition sees 10 amateur celebrity chefs including Alex James (Blur), Keith Duffy (Boyzone) and John Partridge (EastEnders) board a cruise ship and take it in turns to command the kitchen. Their talents will be judged by British celebrity chef and restaurateur Marco Pierre White.




Battlechefs - Series 1, Episode 1


Vigo

Billed as the first ever floating cookery competition Battlechefs is set on board P&O's newest cruise ship Britannia. Greg Rutherford, Jason Gardiner, Deborah Stephenson, Alex James and Jenny Eclair visit Vigo in Spain and learn to cook octopus. But will the Captain be impressed?


Original Air Date: 04-Apr-2016
